reviews.text:
Having sat with this one for a while, I can confirm that in its first week of life, this is indeed a fairly realistic watermelon with no harshness. After about 2 weeks, it goes through an interesting transformation. The vanilla notes in the marshmallow come out to play, and you get a vibrant, juicy, borderline candied, yet realistic watermelon. And this is in a pod system i'm tasting this!&#xD;
&#xD;
Great stuff!
